Para atasan mendukung istriku.

262
00:16:51,980 --> 00:16:54,020
Penting bagiku.

263
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:56,720
Terima kasih.

264
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:59,690
Jika ada yang perlu dengan detektif sungguhan...

265
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:02,090
...aku ada di ruangan berkas.

266
00:17:04,990 --> 00:17:07,460
Detektif kambing hitam datang melapor.

267
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:10,430
Mereka bilang kau akan bergabung.

268
00:17:10,470 --> 00:17:13,970
Masuk. Kau bisa mulai.

269
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,970
Di sana.

270
00:17:16,010 --> 00:17:19,310
Bagaimana kemajuannya dengan pacarmu?

271
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:23,310
Pagi ini, tiba-tiba saja
dia menyatakan cintanya padaku.

272
00:17:23,350 --> 00:17:24,410
Oh!

273
00:17:24,450 --> 00:17:25,480
Kau menyatakan balik?

274
