278
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:35,990
Oh!

279
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:37,790
Apa ini, kasus wanita dalam tong?

280
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:40,900
Ditaruh di bagian 'menakutkan'?
